section normed_group

variables {ùïú : Type*} [normed_field ùïú] [star_ring ùïú]
variables [topological_space Œ±] [normed_group Œ≤] [star_add_monoid Œ≤] [normed_star_monoid Œ≤]
variables [normed_space ùïú Œ≤] [star_module ùïú Œ≤]

